
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Esgela.com - Login</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body class="font-sans">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="bg-black text-white shadow-md">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold flex items-center">
                <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-black px-2 py-1 rounded-sm mr-2">e</span>
                Sgela.com
            </a>
            <ul class="hidden md:flex space-x-6 text-sm">
                <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-400">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-400">Courses</a></li>
                <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-400">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login" class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold">Login</a></li>
                <li><a href="/register" class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold">Apply</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Section -->
    <main class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-6 lg:px-20 py-16">
        <!-- Form Section -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-center text-gray-800">Welcome Back</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6 text-center">Login with your ID or Student number and password</p>
            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <label for="identifier" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">ID / Student Number</label>
                <input type="text" id="identifier" name="identifier" required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md mb-4 focus:outline-none focus:border-black">

                <label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md mb-4 focus:outline-none focus:border-black">

                <!-- Display message (dynamic server-side message) -->
                <span class="text-red-500 block mb-4"><%= message %></span>

                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                    <a href="/admin" class="text-sm italic font-semibold text-black  hover:text-gray-700 transition">Admin Login</a>
                </div>

                <button type="submit"
                    class="w-full bg-black text-white py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-800 transition duration-300">Login</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0 lg:ml-16 max-w-xl text-center lg:text-left">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">Why Esgela?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Access accredited online courses</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Learn from top instructors and industry experts</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Track your progress and get certified</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Join a growing community of learners</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-8 p-4 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 bg-yellow-50 rounded">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 italic">“Esgela has transformed the way I learn. The platform is easy to use, and the content is top-notch!”</p>
                <p class="mt-2 font-bold text-sm text-gray-700">— Simanga Luxolo, Software Development Student</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
